121
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:06,400
Th-This time, we're finished for sure!

122
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:09,610
Now that Gohan, who we were
depending on, has wound up like that...

123
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:43,060
