<i>Gather up your energy, (substitutes are okay),</i>

134
00:23:19,490 --> 00:23:22,080
<i>Come over here, lai, lai, lai.</i>

135
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:29,580
<i>Ooh, miracle ZENKAI power!</i>

136
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:33,670
<i>A hungry, naughty Kinto Un,</i>

137
00:23:33,710 --> 00:23:35,470
<i>A mountain full of horizons.</i>

138
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:39,510
<i>They meet each other, they come apart,</i>
<i>they meet each other, they come apart, Oh, no!</i>

139
00:23:39,550 --> 00:23:45,180
<i>Aah, enough! Even Kami-sama has it rough.</i>

140
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:47,350
<i>So sorry.</i>

141
00:23:47,390 --> 00:23:52,520
<i>Ooh, full-bellied ZENKAI power!</i>

142
00:23:55,230 --> 00:24:00,530
<i>Come on out, full-on ZENKAI power!</i>

143
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,090
<i>Heya! I'm Goku!</i>

144
00:24:14,130 --> 00:24:18,180
<i>Gohan, don't you dare give up!</i>
<i>Believe in your own power!</i>

145
00:24:18,220 --> 00:24:20,300
<i>Right now, you are the</i>
<i>strongest one in the universe!</i>

146
00:24:20,340 --> 00:24:23,770
<i>Damn, Gohan's ki is weaker than Cell's.</i>

147
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:25,930
<i>The way things are going,</i>
<i>he's going to be done in.</i>

148
00:24:25,970 --> 00:24:27,940
<i>Next time on Dragon Ball Z,</i>

149
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:31,770
<i>"From Goku to Gohan...</i>
<i>The Spirit of the Father is Handed Down."</i>

150
